strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36098ca555c3cb037b2601044b1566a8662c9ee4","tid":1541620,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QgnuQOg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQgnuQOg.jpg&h=5fff8b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9月6號，全民戴裝日<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊戴頭盔、口罩、眼罩，目的係提醒大家行街坐車都會隨時被襲擊，扑頭、噴椒、或身處毒霧環境，所以要戴上防具作象徵，靜默地抗議。<br />\n<br />\n以下幾點提議比番大家:<br />\n1. 番學番工放工時間做，越多人做效果越好，人多亦唔易比人check身份證<br />\n2. 行街坐車行商場都戴住，唔使怕奇怪，因為更無理既事日日都發生緊<br />\n3. 番工裝扮未必帶到頭盔，但唔戴都帶住，作為一個象徵，又或者只帶口罩眼罩<br />\n4. 真勇武就小心，比人check身份證留record就麻煩<br />\n5. 只帶防具，只係要保護自己，唔好有其他可疑裝備<br />\n<br />\n當人人都有頭盔口罩係身既時候，就可以淡化帶gear本身既奇怪，保護大家，亦比一份支持勇武。"},{"pid":"006013e7f44089a1281001eb56e3df61468c1496","tid":1541620,"uid":114673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b1f1f9b635d22666c9b48e89e408c1a5d50de62","tid":1541620,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:35:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef31f42a7020567c9fc01874be45736a5811260b","tid":1541620,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:35:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f46ebca969861a271aabdcdc7d7719bb73707f8","tid":1541620,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:58:42.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"b8864b3fc572f0bfe28d2a8d0e6440ac8d82b399","tid":1541620,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:06:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7e400bfcd6a91dae6a6747b62ac58a183622c2d","tid":1541620,"uid":57062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:25:59.000Z","msg":"戴口罩！ 戴口罩！"},{"pid":"58f20b14bced5d75ea982f4841489047e879c674","tid":1541620,"uid":20753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"推呀 見唔到人戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}